# Task #124: the post-launch push hook draws nothing (the launcher owns the screen again),
# so an engine PAIRING_EXPIRED (exit 6) there must still surface — by writing the shared
# .pairing-expired flag the Tools-menu banner reads. The hook itself must stay exit-0.
desc post-launch hook (#124): --push-save rc=6 writes the pairing-expired flag silently
invoke posthook
config paired
romarg Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda.gba
sdfile+ Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda.gba
engine 6|PAIRING_EXPIRED
expect_exit 0
expect_trace ENGINE --push-save
expect_file .userdata/shared/Lodor/.pairing-expired
